he priesthood of Moses and Aaron, and the peace offerings of Samuel.  \u8594\'3f
\par According as Thou didst accept of thy holy apostles this true ministry, receive thus also from the hands of us sinners these gifts in Thy goodness, O Lord; that having been vouchsafed t
